Add the butter
minced garlic to a deep skillet
Add the milk to the skillet along with the cream cheese
Adding Parmesan
Season the sauce with salt and pepper.
Add the fresh spinach to the sauce.
Boil a pot of hot water.
Add the pasta and cook until al dense.
Drain the pasta in a colander.
add the cooked and drained pasta to the spinach alfredo sauce.
